data.description:
Charming 3-Bedroom Home on 2.1 Acres with Pool and Upgrades!

Welcome to your dream home in the heart of Long Beach, Mississippi! This beautiful single-story residence offers 2,775 square feet of comfortable living space, featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and a host of amenities that make it the perfect place to call home.

This home boasts a generous living area that's perfect for both relaxation and entertainment. The front sitting room welcomes guests with its warm and inviting ambiance, while the large living room provides ample space for gatherings with family and friends.

The dining area is the perfect setting for enjoying meals with loved ones or hosting dinner parties. It's conveniently located for easy access from the kitchen.

Step outside to your own outdoor paradise. Enjoy warm Mississippi days by the pool, where you can cool off and soak up the sun. The 2.1-acre lot offers plenty of room to explore, play, or even start your own garden!
A handy storage shed on the property provides extra space for tools, equipment, or hobby storage.

This home has been lovingly maintained and features various upgrades including fresh paint, flooring, updated bathroom and more!

Located in the desirable Long Beach area, incredibly close to I-10 interstate, you'll have easy access to all the amenities the town has to offer, including schools, shopping, dining, and the beautiful Gulf Coast beaches. It's a peaceful retreat with the convenience of city living.

Don't miss this incredible opportunity to own a spacious, upgraded home on a substantial 2.1-acre lot in Long Beach, Mississippi. Schedule a showing today and start making lasting memories in this wonderful property!
